8a0b603eb4ad57.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>破译鬼的真名</strong>：找到对应的圣器，在祭坛封印它——手速慢？小心鬼暴走！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/5c0affe1dcc8b813e4d6855eb58a54e3.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逃命大作战</strong>：恶魔一开猎杀，立刻奔跑、躲柜子！还能用圣经逼退恶魔，超解气！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️ 为啥好玩？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物理互动</strong>：推开柜门、接听电话、弹奏钢琴……场景真实随便玩！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>语音交流</strong>：边跑边和队友互动，被猎杀死后还能变成魂体给队友线索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>金币狂赚</strong>：完成驱魔任务拿金币，买玩具熊面具、天使翅膀阿凡达形象，打扮成最靓的抓鬼达人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.poster.avif?t=1751451925\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.webm?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194220/extras/66263d67ebfdbaa91467a6aec395b680.mp4?t=1751451925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️ 免费也能爽：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >古宅地图+经典模式，和小伙伴一起联机、够你玩通宵！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加Discord解锁<strong>疯狂模式</strong>，挑战<strong>10种动态恶魔能力</strong>！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☠️ 如果你沉迷于……</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Animal Company》、《Noclip VR》和《Yeeps》的疯狂追逐快感——我们的动态猎杀系统将让你肾上腺素飙升！恶魔会攀爬、破门，甚至伪装突袭。</p>",
